          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1717410128774-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1 min</p><p>Once the shallot has softened, add your <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong> and cook for 5-7 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1598257627691-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1598257627691-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1598257627691-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1598257627691-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1598257627691-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel your <strong>ginger</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half and scrape the seeds out with a spoon</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, reserving some leaves for garnish</p><p>Add the<strong> ginger</strong>,<strong> garlic</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of<strong> </strong>the <strong>chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>Thai green curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1602153140264-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1602153140264-x400.jpg",
