          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1602153140264-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Thai green curry paste</strong> to the pan with the chicken and cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, add your<strong> fish sauce</strong> with your<strong> lime leaf[ves]</strong>, the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>fragrant stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1598259046715-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1598259046715-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1598259046715-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1598259046715-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1598259046715-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped green beans</strong> and <strong>fragrant stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened - this is your <strong>Thai green chicken thigh curry</strong></p><p>Tip: Add an extra splash of water if the sauce thickens too quickly!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1598257711743-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1598257711743-x400.jpg",
